data.description: Renovated in 2012, This 2 family property offers has tremendous potential for investment or to live in. Located in University Heights, each unit boasts 2 bedrooms and 1 bathroom. The property also features a full, partially finished basement with a separate entrance and an unfinished attic ripe with potential for expansion or customization. The spacious backyard, easily accessible from the first floor or through a secure gate is great for a private retreat just waiting for customization. One block away from Orange Street Light rail station makes commuting effortless. The property is also minutes away from serene Branch Brook Park. Come see it for yourself before it gone!
